{"tid":1434404,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我係由2047年坐時光機黎，想知點解2019年反送中會失敗","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T15:02:14.000Z","uid":54930,"like":16,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ab379d62d212f85b5f625bbe169673ed07abd26","tid":1434404,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:35:56.000Z","msg":"反送中失敗後<br />\n民主運動 一蹶不振<br />\n幾年後香港納入中國網絡長城範圍<br />\n從此任何敏感資訊都睇唔到<br />\n而家我果邊2047年，政府準備宣布改名香港市同正式拆關<br />\n剩底土生土長既香港人打算同政府決一死戰<br />\n佢地唔想重蹈覆轍<br />\n所以開戰前送左我黎2019年<br />\n要我問你地，發生左咩事導致失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a0efec2e69f7a40158f95afc47bb34b8fe92d2","tid":1434404,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e76dd46aef84b164e0659fdf61345774cef27b","tid":1434404,"uid":179402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:37:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「幫幫手推一推」黑警唔單止搜身時恐嚇市民 仲要強光照市民對眼！ | LIHKG</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=770da565\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=7be47b3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有乜野必要同理由對市民使用強光照住佢對眼？呢個行為有咩意義同對工作上有咩幫助？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">強烈要求黑警回應點解要用惡劣 粗暴 令人不適嘅態度 語氣 行為 去對待配合黑警工作嘅市民！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手派出去 推上報<br />\n<br />\n今次拍片者冇事 下個好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9811b6fbc9025629dafd44b5351f77a9982759d","tid":1434404,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:42:06.000Z","msg":"我知呢次打擊大家都好灰<br />\n但我需要搵出真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34f2e3135bb252a5d13691b1595a236442a17ed","tid":1434404,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:50:47.000Z","msg":"p.s.我係偷入我老豆既ac<br />\n因為佢個連登ac同pw都<br />\n同佢個香港社會信用(Xiang Gang Social Credit)一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n另外唔該搵人快d答我<br />\n我需要係佢發現之前返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f07b544af94d371c7b46c291593e0e1ee760f83","tid":1434404,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:54:10.000Z","msg":"唔該<br />\n2047年既香港人需要你地講出真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afbfc181309221830170f42c6d1ef7fbb450e6c","tid":1434404,"uid":191713,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:10:27.000Z","msg":"你地未來人都唔知我地點知"},{"pid":"ad0b4f8f98ac26342e854f46f78aca41629c3e45","tid":1434404,"uid":266172,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:17:03.000Z","msg":"Hi, I am from 2047 as well.<br />\nI desperately need a IBM5100 to go back to my timeline.<br />\nDo you know where I can obtain one in Hong Kong?<br />\n<br />\nRegards,<br />\nJohn Titor"},{"pid":"2845db68ecf7f648920e55ffce5392a6d98ed22e","tid":1434404,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"發生咩事呀？邊個玩我連登ac？邊個咁大整蠱？&nbsp;"},{"pid":"d0d3f02797a2da026a4d7bce9270644cd555aea8","tid":1434404,"uid":